Apres chris ❄️🎿🥳🎅

Happy 50th birthday. We are having the best time celebrating you and doing your favorite things (skiing at stowe and now headed to the BVIs to sail for the week) with our families. An unexpected thing happened when I met chris. I found the love of a lifetime.  Not only did a find true love but I found myself. This love was something I have never came across. There is no one more loving, thoughtful, supportive, unconditional or fun. The life we have lived in the past 8 years is because of our friendship and love for one another. i want 50 more. Life with you just keeps getting better and being married to you is way better than a fairytale. I love you.

Thank you 2023 ✨

2024, we’re ready for you!
